{"type":"message","id":"02990685","parentId":"950c3ada","timestamp":"2026-05-14T10:06:18.563Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ET_Lj0eXky6gCWhdz2FBFd90121","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"plans\":[{\"group\":0,\"name\":\"Undefined\",\"sdks\":[]},{\"group\":2,\"name\":\"TapTap\",\"sdks\":[\"GuanFang\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\",\"TapTapNew\"]},{\"group\":3,\"name\":\"FiveChannel\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":4,\"name\":\"Steam\",\"sdks\":[\"SteamGiant\",\"CrashSight_PC\"]},{\"group\":11,\"name\":\"GuanFangIOS\",\"sdks\":[\"GuanFang\",\"GASDK_IOS\",\"FaceBook\",\"CrashSight_IOS\",\"PerfSightPlugin_IOS\",\"PerfSight_IOS\"]},{\"group\":6,\"name\":\"Activation\",\"sdks\":[\"GASDK_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":7,\"name\":\"OverSea\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"Permission\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":8,\"name\":\"WeGame\",\"sdks\":[\"WeGameGiant\",\"CrashSight_PC\"]},{\"group\":9,\"name\":\"MacGA\",\"sdks\":[\"GuanFang\",\"GASDK_OSX\"]},{\"group\":10,\"name\":\"OneStore\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"OneStore\"]},{\"group\":16,\"name\":\"GuanFangPC\",\"sdks\":[\"GuanFangPC\",\"CrashSight_PC\",\"PerfSightPlugin_PC\",\"PerfSight_PC\"]},{\"group\":12,\"name\":\"TapTapSea\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"TapTapSea\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":13,\"name\":\"FiveChannelJiuYou\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":14,\"name\":\"FiveChannelMiGuYun\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":1,\"name\":\"Google\",\"sdks\":[\"Google\"]},{\"group\":15,\"name\":\"HaoYouKuaiBao\",\"sdks\":[\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"GASDK_Android\",\"GuanFang\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":5,\"name\":\"GuanFang\",\"sdks\":[\"GASDK_Android\",\"GuanFang\",\"CrashSight_Android\",\"PerfSightPlugin_Android\",\"PerfSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":17,\"name\":\"DouYin\",\"sdks\":[\"GASDK_Android\",\"GuanFang\",\"GameAnalytics_Android\",\"CrashSight_Android\"]},{\"group\":0,\"name\":\"Test\",\"sdks\":[\"TapTapNew\"]},{\"group\":18,\"name\":\"BiliBiliPC\",\"sdks\":[\"CrashSight_PC\",\"PerfSight_PC\",\"BiliBiliPC\"]}],\"curPlan\":{\"group\":0,\"name\":\"Undefined\",\"sdks\":[]}}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778753178563}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb188ee5","parentId":"02990685","timestamp":"2026-05-14T10:06:24.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current plan is \"Undefined\" with group 0 and no SDKs. This means:\n1. The GASDK define in the project settings is set at the project level (not coming from the SDK plan)\n2. The GiantSDK files haven't been copied\n\nThe critical issue is: the scripting define symbols in `ProjectSettings.asset` include `GASDK` at line 634 (Standalone - platform 1). This is a hard-coded define in the project settings, not coming from the SDK plan.\n\nThe question is: why would the GASDK define exist in Standalone platform if the GiantSDK files aren't in Assets? This seems like it was set up for the actual release builds.\n\nFor the hot update pipeline (which presumably runs for test server purposes), the pipeline only needs to build asset bundles (not the actual player). The issue is that Unity's script compilation happens before any `-executeMethod` runs, so if the scripts have errors, nothing will work.\n\nI think the best approach here is:\n1. Apply an appropriate SDK plan first (probably one that adds GiantSDK for Standalone), OR\n2. Temporarily remove the GASDK define from the project settings for stand-alone builds, OR\n3. Manually copy the GiantSDK files into Assets\n\nActually, wait - let me re-examine the problem. The `using GiantSDK.Parent;` is guarded by `#if GASDK || STEAMGIANT || WeGame || GUANFANGPC`. The `GASDK` define IS set. But the GiantSDK plugin isn't in Assets. \n\nFor a hot update pipeline, we probably don't need GiantSDK at all for Standalone. Let me check if maybe there's a way to remove the GASDK define. Or maybe I need to copy the GASDK_Android or GASDK_OSX files... but there's a GASDK folder in OtherPlugins, and a GuanFangPC one.\n\nWait, `OtherPlugins\\GASDK\\GiantSDK\\` exists with `namespace GiantSDK.Parent`. But these files are NOT inside Assets. They need to be copied to Assets for the compiler to find them.\n\nLet me look at how the SDK is set up to understand the copy paths.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xhUcF3rElINzJtI60OEQ5919","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\Assets\\Editor\\SDKTool\\Database\\SDKFileBase.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":811,"output":555,"cacheRead":40320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41686,"cost":{"input":0.00011354000000000001,"output":0.0001554,"cacheRead":0.00112896,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013979}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778753178564,"responseId":"27b44f20-04b8-440d-9003-f45ed860265f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f47aab9","parentId":"cb188ee5","timestamp":"2026-05-14T10:06:24.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_xhUcF3rElINzJtI60OEQ5919","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿using System;\nusing System.IO;\n\n\nnamespace SDKTool\n{\n    [Serializable]\n    public class SDKFileBase\n    {\n        public string fromPath;\n        public string toPath;\n\n        public virtual void Setup(string from, string to)\n        {\n        }\n\n        public virtual void CopyTo()\n        {\n            //fromPath为空不拷贝\n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(fromPath)) return;\n            //$开头的路径表示回退时不需要删除\n            string to = toPath;\n            if (toPath.StartsWith(\"$\"))\n            {\n                to = toPath.Substring(1);\n            }\n\n            bool success = false;\n            if (File.Exists(fromPath))\n            {\n                var dir = Path.GetDirectoryName(to);\n                if (!Directory.Exists(dir))\n                {\n                    if (dir != null) Directory.CreateDirectory(dir);\n                }\n\n                File.Copy(fromPath, to, true);\n                success = true;\n            }\n\n            if (Directory.Exists(fromPath))\n            {\n                DirectoryInfo source = new DirectoryInfo(fromPath);\n                DirectoryInfo target = new DirectoryInfo(to);\n\n                if (target.FullName.StartsWith(source.FullName, StringComparison.CurrentCultureIgnoreCase))\n                {\n                    throw new Exception($\"父目录不能拷贝到子目录！fromPath:{fromPath} toPath:{toPath}\");\n                }\n\n                CopyDirectory(fromPath, to, true);\n                success = true;\n            }\n\n            if (success == false) throw new Exception($\"文件{fromPath}不存在！\");\n        }\n\n        public virtual void Revert()\n        {\n            //$开头的路径表示回退时不需要删除\n            if (toPath.StartsWith(\"$\"))\n            {\n                return;\n            }\n\n            if (File.Exists(toPath))\n            {\n                File.Delete(toPath);\n            }\n\n            if (Directory.Exists(toPath))\n            {\n                Directory.Delete(toPath, true);\n                if (File.Exists(toPath + \".meta\"))\n                    File.Delete(toPath + \".meta\");\n            }\n        }\n\n        internal virtual bool CopyDirectory(string source, string target, bool overwrite)\n        {\n            bool ret;\n            try\n            {\n                if (Directory.Exists(source))\n                {\n                    if (Directory.Exists(target) == false)\n                        Directory.CreateDirectory(target);\n\n                    foreach (var file in Directory.GetFiles(source))\n                    {\n                        FileInfo fileInfo = new FileInfo(file);\n                        fileInfo.CopyTo(string.Concat(target, \"/\", fileInfo.Name), overwrite);\n                    }\n\n                    foreach (string dir in Directory.GetDirectories(source))\n                    {\n                        DirectoryInfo directoryInfo = new DirectoryInfo(dir);\n                        if (CopyDirectory(dir, String.Concat(target, \"/\", directoryInfo.Name), overwrite) == false)\n                            ret = false;\n                    }\n                }\n\n                ret = true;\n            }\n            catch (Exception ex)\n            {\n                ret = false;\n            }\n\n            return ret;\n        }\n    }\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778753184882}}
