{"type":"message","id":"addf816f","parentId":"9b09415d","timestamp":"2026-05-14T10:09:11.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The GiantSDK errors are gone (no more `GiantSDK` type not found errors)! But now there are new errors:\n\n1. `ChannelMacro_PerfSight.cs` - uses `PerfSightAgent` which doesn't exist (PerfSight is defined)\n2. `ChannelMacro_CrashSight.cs` - uses `CrashSightAgent` which doesn't exist (CRASH_SIGHT is defined)\n3. `ChannelMacro_GASDK.cs` - uses `mhpsdk` which doesn't exist (GASDK is defined)\n\nThese are all channel SDK references that are conditionally compiled with the define symbols `PerfSight`, `CRASH_SIGHT`, and `GASDK`. The defines are set in the project's scripting defines.\n\nThe root cause is clear: the project has all these SDK defines set but the SDK plugins aren't in the Assets folder. This is a chicken-and-egg problem where the SDK Manager normally copies the plugins into Assets before builds happen, but the hot update pipeline can't compile scripts to even run the SDK manager.\n\nThe cleanest approach is to remove all the SDK-related defines from the Standalone platform (platform 1) so scripts can compile cleanly for the hot update pipeline. The SDK defines are not needed for building asset bundles.\n\nLet me modify the ProjectSettings.asset to remove `GASDK`, `GuanFang`, `CRASH_SIGHT`, and `PerfSight` from platform 1's scripting defines.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"The GiantSDK errors are fixed but there are more missing SDK plugins. The project has all SDK defines active but plugins aren't in Assets. Let me fix the scripting defines for Standalone (platform 1) since this is just a hot update pipeline."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_q0zulgnJSHxb80EgZX5F3176","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\ProjectSettings\\ProjectSettings.asset","edits":[{"oldText":"    1: UNITY_POST_PROCESSING_STACK_V2;AMPLIFY_SHADER_EDITOR;TextMeshPro;GASDK;GuanFang;CRASH_SIGHT;PerfSight","newText":"    1: UNITY_POST_PROCESSING_STACK_V2;AMPLIFY_SHADER_EDITOR;TextMeshPro"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5683,"output":540,"cacheRead":60928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67151,"cost":{"input":0.00079562,"output":0.00015120000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001705984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002652804}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778753344875,"responseId":"ae9fd326-1e3b-4606-bab4-5f480590d631"}}
